    "an10.240-266:0.2": "23. Abbreviated Texts Beginning With Greed ",
    "an10.240-266:0.3": "Untitled Discourses on Greed ",
    "an10.240-266:1.1": "“For the complete understanding of greed … ",
    "an10.240-266:1.2": "complete ending … ",
    "an10.240-266:1.3": "giving up … ",
    "an10.240-266:1.4": "ending … ",
    "an10.240-266:1.5": "vanishing … ",
    "an10.240-266:1.6": "fading away … ",
    "an10.240-266:1.7": "cessation … ",
    "an10.240-266:1.8": "giving away … ",
    "an10.240-266:1.9": "letting go … ",
    "an10.240-266:1.10": "these ten things should be developed.” "
